  "remarks": "\nSanjar ISMAILOV is an involved person within the meaning of the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 because he is associated with a person who is an involved person. ISMAILOV is the nephew of Alisher Usmanov, who was designated by the UK Government on 3 March 2022.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
